	url="https://example.com",
	full_page=False,
	use_persistent=False,
	api_name="/screenshot"
)
print(result)
Accepts 3 parameters:
url str Default: "https://example.com"

The input value that is provided in the "URL" Textbox component.

full_page bool Default: False

The input value that is provided in the "Full Page Screenshot" Checkbox component.

use_persistent bool Default: False

The input value that is provided in the "Use Persistent Browser" Checkbox component.

Returns 1 element
dict(path: str | None (Path to a local file), url: str | None (Publicly available url or base64 encoded image), size: int | None (Size of image in bytes), orig_name: str | None (Original filename), mime_type: str | None (mime type of image), is_stream: bool (Can always be set to False), meta: dict(str, Any))

The output value that appears in the "Screenshot" Image component.

