from gradio_client import Client

client = Client("diamond-in/Browser-Use-mcp")
result = client.predict(
	url1="https://example.com",
	url2="https://example.com/new",
	threshold=0.98,
	api_name="/visual_regression_test"
)
print(result)
Accepts 3 parameters:
url1 str Default: "https://example.com"

The input value that is provided in the "URL 1" Textbox component.

url2 str Default: "https://example.com/new"

The input value that is provided in the "URL 2" Textbox component.

threshold float Default: 0.98

The input value that is provided in the "Similarity Threshold" Slider component.

Returns 1 element
str

The output value that appears in the "Visual Comparison Result" Code component.

